 Open-Label Safety Study of Telaprevir and Sofosbuvir in Chronic Hepatitis C Genotype 1@highlight

This is an open-label, multi center study of treatment-naive non-cirrhotic subjects with genotype 1 chronic Hepatitis C Virus.

 All subjects will receive telaprevir (TVR) in combination with sofosbuvir (SOF) for 12 weeks.

